{"tid":2445840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雍景台殷樺花園1,855人強制檢測 無人確診 外籍居民批警無法交代詳情","createTime":"2021-03-14T03:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T05:20:01.000Z","uid":239336,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"17b3282cda46db289855a22f8ecd12e583191665","tid":2445840,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"政府周六（13日）晚上突襲封半山干德道56號殷樺花園第一、二期，及羅便臣道雍景台第一、二座強制檢測。大批警員先抵達雍景台，並於雍景台行車閘口拉封鎖線，未幾殷樺花園第二座亦已拉上橙帶，阻止居民離開。政府今早9時完成強制檢測行動，並指截至凌晨2時，共有1,855名居民接受檢測，當中沒有確診個案。封區期間，政府派員到訪約980戶，當中約150戶沒人應門，政府會再跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">而昨晚封區時，封鎖區外有不少外籍人士聚集，有外籍人士表示對住所附近突然被封感非常愕然，指曾向在場警員查詢區域內的情況不果，被逼在附近的街道上流連，感到非常不滿，指警員應起碼交代清楚發生甚麼事（You will at least have to tell me what&rsquo;s going on, that&rsquo;s really basic!）。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5_bP63DLq5EbpNdnXnV87KEkRmk=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CLX3IEFKPZH7RD3EAU3TPSB5SU.jfif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5_bP63DLq5EbpNdnXnV87KEkRmk%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCLX3IEFKPZH7RD3EAU3TPSB5SU.jfif&h=e3ca6756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有外籍人士於殷樺花園第二座門口與警員理論，稱只曾於大廈逗留約一小時，理應不必進行檢測，惟經過一番理論後似乎爭取不果，又再度回到大廈內。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210313/SS7BPSXMARCKLOCD7APA2HXYIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210313%2FSS7BPSXMARCKLOCD7APA2HXYIQ%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c832335b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210313%2FSS7BPSXMARCKLOCD7APA2HXYIQ%2F&h=6ee8ee8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210313/SS7BPSXMARCKLOCD7APA2HXYIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"bad4b7fc85363447503bd60aff40e81e49ac3203",